<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Add support for explicit namespace.name =&gt; function/method mapping.</p>

<p>Similar in nature to:</p>

<p><a href="http://scripts.incutio.com/xmlrpc/basic-server-construction.php">http://scripts.incutio.com/xmlrpc/â€¦</a></p>

<p>Essentially, expected api:</p>

<p>$server-&gt;addMethod($functionName, $functionMethodCallback);</p>

<p>if ($this) was passed in $functionmethodCallback, the server SHOULD NOT attempt to clone or recreate the object, instead it should map the call the to already passed in object.  This will be useful when embedding an XMLRPC server inside a controllers action.</p>

<p>Addionally, if a valid callback is presented as strings, an object should be created.</p>

<p>For more info, contact me if need be.</p>

